text: Keith McPhillamy (20 June 1882 - 3 May 1937) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class match for New South Wales in 1904/05. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1882 births Category:1937 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
